. * 3d. 手动做一遍带 SMD（standardized mean difference）的均衡检查
. *     SMD 是匹配文献的核心指标（|SMD|<0.1 一般认为均衡）
. di as text _n "Standardized Mean Differences:"

Standardized Mean Differences:

. foreach v in age educ black hispan married nodegree re74 re75 {
  2.     qui sum `v' if treat == 1
  3.     local m1 = r(mean)
  4.     local sd1 = r(sd)
  5.     qui sum `v' if treat == 0
  6.     local m0 = r(mean)
  7.     local sd0 = r(sd)
  8.     local smd = (`m1' - `m0') / sqrt((`sd1'^2 + `sd0'^2)/2)
  9.     qui ttest `v', by(treat)
 10.     di as text "  `v': diff=" %9.3f (`m1'-`m0')         "  SMD=" %7.3f `sm
> d' "  p=" %6.4f r(p)
 11. }
